Prepare data for normalization

Source: R/metabolomics_computation.R
met.PreparePrenormData.Rd

met.PreparePrenormData checks for previous data editing and filtering, and defines adds a 'prenormalization' data table to the mSet object for further analysis.

Usage

met.PreparePrenormData(mSetObj = NA)

Arguments

mSetObj

Enter name of the created mSet object (see met.read_data).

Value

The input mSet object with prenorm data table at mSetObj$dataSet$prenorm.

References

adapted from PreparePrenormData (https://github.com/xia-lab/MetaboAnalystR).
